                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.61
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The thick target was simply",
                "prepared by compressing C13-enriched lampblack into a",
                "3/8-in. recess milled in a silver blank. Preparation",
                "of very thin targets of high uniformity was achieved",
                "by \"cracking\" a hydrocarbon vapor or gas on a heated",
                "metal surface, leaving an adherent film of carbon.",
                "While the \"background\" is taken with a normal",
                " (98.9 percent C12) fraction."
              ]
